726445f-a.title: Queens: Cross Island Bouleva - 15th Avenue
726445f-a.text:
Cross Island Boulevard, east side, north of 15th Avenue, showing St. Nicholas Greek Orthodox Church. View 2 is south from the Long Island Railroad tracks and shows the First Church of Christ, Scientist, to the right of St. Nicholas Church. Cross Island Boulevard, here, is a viaduct over the railroad tracks.
P. L. Sperr  March 5, 1932
VUS 1,
